# Task Documentation Required Before Implementation

Before starting any implementation, write a task document in `doc/tasks/` describing the change. Link the document in PR description.

## Requirements
- File location: `doc/tasks/{kebab-case-task-name}.md`
- Include: goal, scope, acceptance criteria, risks, rollout plan.
- Reference relevant files using `mdc:` links for clarity.

## Template
Use the template: [doc/tasks/task-template.md](mdc:doc/tasks/task-template.md)